data.description: Located in the heart of Ammon, this home offers main floor living with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, including a master bath. Featuring two fireplaces, refinished hardwood floors, new windows, and updated electrical and plumbing, it boasts a beautiful 1/3 acre yard with mature fruit trees, a shed, and a garden area. Additional highlights include a newer roof, window coverings, water heater, and furnace. Move-in ready with potential for sweat equity, the house has gas heat, central A/C, and an enclosed sunroom that could serve as a great family room. Enjoy the quiet neighborhood, oversized yard, sprinkler system, and garden area, making it ideal for summer entertaining. The partially finished basement offers opportunities to add another bedroom and bath, making the possibilities limitless.
